<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Hello Srija, Pave your path in our Culinary world!!</h2>
    <h1>Dashboard</h1>
    <div class="menu py-5 bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-5 justify-content-center">
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
              <img src="images/food.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Food">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Food</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Look up about different ingredients, its nutritional value and possible recipes with it.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
              <img src="images/quiz.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Quiz">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Quiz</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Take a quiz to know your current preferred food ingredients without thinking much about it!</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
              <img src="images/search_recipe.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Search Recipe">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Search Recipes</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Get to know different recipes using specific ingredients.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
              <img src="images/cuisine.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Cuisine">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Cuisine</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Get to know about different recipes from unique cuisines.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
              <img src="images/meal.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Meal">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Meal</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Finding it hard to decide what to have for Breakfast, Lunch or Dinner? Know what recipes are healthy and mostly eaten at different food time zones.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
